-------------------------------------
FilePeruser Installation Instructions
-------------------------------------

1. Verify you meet the requirements in the README.
2. Follow these steps:
    a. cd to program directory (an "open terminal here" tool works, too)
    b. run cmake to configure the program (ccmake or cmake-gui work well for this)
    c. run `make` (or whatever your system's make executable is called)
    d. run `sudo make install` (or another form of make install, especially on MS systems).
    e. use the program
